{"tid":2018730,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家切勿浪費時間表演自己有幾失望，ig出個全黑po就當自己做左野。做實際的事吧，擴大黃色版圖吧","createTime":"2020-05-15T20:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T04:54:02.000Z","uid":239819,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"26158985d5f2f32684cd67b8df428ff130ca52bf","tid":2018730,"uid":239819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T20:06:08.000Z","msg":"知道大家被今日的新聞搞到好泄氣，但大家唔洗灰心絕望。亦唔好浪費時間表演自己有幾失望，ig出個全黑po就當自己做左野<br />\n<br />\n你其實仲有好多<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更實際的事</span></span>可以做<br />\n<br />\n咁點做呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一） 今日有好幾件事發生，其中一件危中有機的，係歷史科提及日本侵華一事，令大家意識到毛澤東呢個千古罪人講過乜野。我完全覺得呢個係好好的切入點，去令大家身邊的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">藍絲轉黃</span></span>。 <br />\n<br />\n就我個人所見，藍絲往往都係被中共的愛國主義蒙騙。左一句中國人，右一句漢奸就完全否定大家做既一切。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">與其一開始同佢地去解釋何謂五大訴求或三權分立，倒不如順著對方簡單的愛國思維，話比佢知其實支持共產黨，反而是漢奸的表現</span></span></span>，繼而令佢地慢慢意識到<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">愛國=/=愛黨</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">切斷佢地愛國=愛黨的邏輯謬誤</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n我所以話，毛澤東感覺侵華的言論係好好的切入點。<br />\n然後要靠大家開始多讀歷史了。<br />\n例如引述下中共721抗日方針（不是元朗721）、 西安事變等 ，都係有力的証明<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中共借抗日為名，壯大自己實力為實</span></span>，所謂抗日根本是偽裝的，目的是讓日本人殺害國民黨人，殘害同胞。最後，今日的所謂中華人民共和國，其實是這個不義的手段奪取得來。倘若講到咁，藍絲都仲係撐中共，你不妨再講埋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文革中共又殘害了幾千萬中國人</span></span>，數字比二戰死亡人數仲要多。<br />\n<br />\n講咁多，目的只有一個，就係讓藍絲知道，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">中共先係真正的漢奸。邊個到今時今日仲要撐中共，邊個就係殘害同胞的漢奸。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我想澄清，叫大家咁做<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔係要大家做大中華膠或認同自己係咪中國人身份</span></span>，而係只係想大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">打破藍絲的愛國情懷，撕開中共的真面目</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有幸改變到佢地對中共的睇法，不再盲撐，先再慢慢講何謂五大訴求吧。<br />\n<br />\n第二）另一個我覺得可行的切入點，係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">港共派1萬蚊</span></span>。但其實可以話比藍絲知，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地本身有7萬，但香港政府起大白象，送錢比人洗，搞到我地大家都無左一大忽肉</span></span>。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">出來遊行示威，都係想拎返應得的，又點會係搞事？</span></span>。針唔拮到肉唔知痛，派錢咁切身既問題，我覺得可以一試做論點。<br />\n<br />\n條數點計？5000億除700萬人 = 大約每人7萬蚊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/12289549_886202478132040_4055050122763178324_n_lj4ky_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F12289549_886202478132040_4055050122763178324_n_lj4ky_1200x0.png&h=9b55ae57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n總結係，站在對方的位置去思考，用新既方式去說明，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我覺得總好過我地不斷重覆黑警死全家</span></span>--對方聽不明，更聽不入耳。因為就算黑警死全家，只要中共不滅，都係無用，都係會製造另一批黑警。所以，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天滅中共</span></span>更加重要。<br />\n<br />\n不少藍絲其實都係好人，林夕係鏗鏘集都有講過，只係一時被中共曚騙啫，要靠大家努力了。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n實際的事仲有好多，不妨參考下呢位ching的po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2017984/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2017984/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"dc815dd16ba812d8c542c1fe233d8eea29ef4d39","tid":2018730,"uid":239819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T20:06:52.000Z","msg":"我自推"},{"pid":"dab4e2fb4296bd51b1f8a94601f1781882e154c6","tid":2018730,"uid":239819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T20:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8806253dc00750a93cd5f4071e32dde99a68e5ef","tid":2018730,"uid":239819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T20:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9b7d63be0663316197f0bc02f04044a0946157","tid":2018730,"uid":294766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T20:09:04.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"4521d1c884b3ca76e3795cb71b3262ed6bdc25ea","tid":2018730,"uid":294766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T20:09:30.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"2e9347697082304f1f843f2f86be91f0a0f31a66","tid":2018730,"uid":218301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T20:19:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c32690a596fc2b06f4cf1f0e434fc3fe013edcac","tid":2018730,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8f453f63e851ed5776e03c83a6b809fcafee4a","tid":2018730,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:50:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e6caeeb738c63ce11af851345516e5ef386220","tid":2018730,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303b9765da3ea00045d71f03017851f26942b9c9","tid":2018730,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ac0e54957ab9ed947924c2e967e20724f1b880","tid":2018730,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}